item.description:
今天为了偷懒又往 .vimrc 里面写了点东西，作用是在删除类似于()这种成对出现的字符对的前一个字符时同时删除后面那个&hellip;
下面是具体内容:
inoremap &lt;BS&gt; &lt;c-r&gt;=DelPair()&lt;CR&gt;function DelPair() let currentline = getline(&#39;.&#39;) let prechar = currentline[col(&#39;.&#39;) - 2] let fochar = currentline[col(&#39;.&#39;) - 1] if (prechar == &#39;(&#39; &amp;&amp; fochar == &#39;)&#39;) \ || (prechar == &#39;[&#39; &amp;&amp; fochar == &#39;]&#39;) \ || (prechar == &#39;&lt;&#39; &amp;&amp; fochar == &#39;&gt;&#39;) \ || (prechar == &#39;{&#39; &amp;&amp; fochar == &#39;}&#39;) \ || (prechar == &#39;&#34;&#39; &amp;&amp; fochar == &#39;&#34;&#39;) \ || (prechar == &#34;&#39;&#34; &amp;&amp; fochar == &#34;&#39;&#34;) return &#34;\&lt;BS&gt;\&lt;Delete&gt;&#34; else return &#34;\&lt;BS&gt;&#34; endifendf
